{"tid":1859200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有救喇！ 內地臨床測試新藥或有助治新型冠狀病毒","createTime":"2020-02-03T06:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T02:36:48.000Z","uid":171385,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d08974a43303b36930f393028812c7529fbed08e","tid":1859200,"uid":171385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T06:33:01.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】在北京的中日友好醫院今日開始臨床測試新藥「瑞德西韋」，治療新型冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n新英格蘭醫學雜誌在有關美國首宗確診個案的報道中曾提到，名為「瑞德西韋」的藥物，據報有患者接受靜脈注射後病情好轉。<br />\n<br />\n中日友好醫院周一起就瑞德西韋，對武漢的270名確診患者進行臨床三期測試，以確認其安全性和藥效，預計在4月27日結束。<br />\n<br />\n有報道指，美國總統特朗普特別批准同意將瑞德西韋的專利豁免，向中國緊急公開藥物分子結構，直至4月27日。<br />\n<br />\n瑞德西韋是由美國吉利德科學公司針對伊波拉病毒研發，已完成第一、二期的臨床測試，未獲任何國家批准上市。據報瑞德西韋可抑制流行性和人畜共患的冠狀病毒，專家強調今次測試屬新藥研究，必須謹慎處理測試結果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=379130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379130&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KcwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=758e27e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379130&h=6a810da7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=379130</a>"},{"pid":"c1b4db5e7130caee6e210dd95b02914a7a820a4d","tid":1859200,"uid":227271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T06:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNoWOsO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNoWOsO.jpg&h=907de14a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0fbb85ee5d428538d6bfc15ed1d35dba64d5f61","tid":1859200,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T06:35:08.000Z","msg":"日撚日有幾篇呢D新聞"},{"pid":"413676990b0f36afd36f2f1070b90a5576d086ba","tid":1859200,"uid":55955,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T06:36:37.000Z","msg":"侵：美國人條命好珍貴，有人幫我試藥緊係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"224c9a216705dbe2